{
  "stem": "9898.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, a German SS soldier brought to our ambulatory an infant, two to three weeks old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, take care of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I put the baby-- I told the nurse, put the baby in the small room and give him something to drink.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that next day came in an officer of the SS, a tall guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was probably 6' 2', 6' 3'.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was asked, who is in charge?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I am in charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he went in the small room and found the baby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He got so angry, so mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He started screaming, what is this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said-- in German, I knew German very well-- I said, sir, a German soldier brought the baby to take care of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he started to screaming, this is a Jew!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is one!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Take him immediately out to the trains!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I asked one the nurses to go out with me to the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I took the baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is the first time I was out on the Umschlagplatz to see how they're loading, what are they doing there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "To describe this is beyond any imagination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, Dante wrote This is worse than hell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was worse than hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The screaming, the pushing, the beating, the shooting, the killing, the wild dogs tearing people apart-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I will never get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] We gave the baby-- they were pushing 200 people into one wagon-- into one car, where only 50 or 60 maximum could get in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember the nurse gave the baby to one lady standing in front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then suddenly, I saw from the left side approaching us, running, around 25 or 30 yeshiva students.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
